Package: flaticron
Architecture: all
Depends: bsd-mailx, flatpak, systemd, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Send mail notifications for pending Flatpak updates
 flaticron sends emails about pending Flatpak updates.
 The package provides a systemd unit with a timer running once a day to
 automate the check for available Flatpak updates.

